{"tid":2231194,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"愛不是義務，而是表演 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-10-05T13:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T13:06:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"27846fcc7595e9c91a6f7fa9b1c3b482fb039b99","tid":2231194,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T13:06:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201005/CGUG7UBIN5E4FJMRIVZORJXS2Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201005%2FCGUG7UBIN5E4FJMRIVZORJXS2Q%2F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=54da3db3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201005%2FCGUG7UBIN5E4FJMRIVZORJXS2Q%2F&h=4741c8bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201005/CGUG7UBIN5E4FJMRIVZORJXS2Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n愛不是義務，而是表演 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-esT8ppdLN8RpZVvQj5Pqt6JSLU=/1017x565/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FRH6ZWKHABAOBFO5QRD5CIJRH4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-esT8ppdLN8RpZVvQj5Pqt6JSLU%3D%2F1017x565%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFRH6ZWKHABAOBFO5QRD5CIJRH4.png&h=23f2c9f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中聯辦主任駱惠寧在出席中秋酒會時提出，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n此後一天，駱惠寧透過中聯辦發稿，說他落區探訪基層巿民，向他們派發月餅及防疫物資。鏡頭前出現的兩位被探訪者，一個是住小西灣的74歲長者，另一個是住深水埗劏房的失業中年漢。前者送出11萬私己錢，託駱惠寧轉交中國抗疫。後者劏房中最搶眼的則是一幅中國國旗。一個用錢愛中國；一個把中國國旗掛在牀邊，沒有錢就用心去愛中國，都是駱惠寧口中行「正道」的人，大約詮釋了駱惠寧那句「愛國是義務」吧。<br />\n<br />\n有趣的是，相片一出街，馬上被眼利的網民發現劏房失業中年漢為頗受建制媒體歡迎的「愛國護旗手」。所謂「香港基層巿民」，其實來自湖南，不知道有沒有三粒星身份證。<br />\n<br />\n劏房漢在中國有物業，卻情願來香港住劏房，到了香港之後，卻把中國國旗掛在牀頭。如此愛法，真是可歌可泣，催人淚下。但在香港人眼中，卻更似一場愛的表演。<br />\n<br />\n每個人對愛的理解都不一樣，。。。。。。。"}]}